WEBVTT

NOTE
This video is silent. Captions describe what's happening in each scene
so the experience is equivalent for users who can't see the video.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
A student joins a classroom over video. An ASL interpreter signs from a remote office.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:08.000
The Virtual VRI logo: Video Remote Interpreting.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:13.000
A man in a flannel shirt signs at home, on a video call.

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:18.000
A boardroom meeting. The remote ASL interpreter joins on a laptop.

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:23.000
A medical visit. The interpreter is on screen, signing for the patient.

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Real interpreters. Real conversations. Virtual VRI — Video Remote Interpreting.
